Class Quad

  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Image

    public class Quad
extends DisplayObject
    A Quad represents a rectangle with a uniform color or a color gradient. You can set one color per vertex. The colors will smoothly fade into each other over the area of the quad. To display a simple linear color gradient, assign one color to vertices 0 and 1 and another color to vertices 2 and 3.
